question: In which department is Ms. Brant?
query: PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?deptLabel WHERE { <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/dept-73191> rdfs:label ?deptLabel . }

question: What is the telephone of Baldwin Dirksen?
query: PREFIX : <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT ?agent WHERE { ?agent a :Agent ; :phone ?telephone . FILTER (STRSTARTS(STR(?agent), 'http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/empl-Baldwin.Dirksen@company.org')) }

question: Who is the manager of Heinrich Hoch?
query: PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?manager WHERE { <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/empl-Heinrich.Hoch@company.org> <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/hasManager> ?manager .}

question: What is the email of Sabrina from Marketing?
query: PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT ?email WHERE { <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/empl-Sabrina.Geiger%40company.org> ns1:email ?email . }

question: Who has expertise in Transistors?
query: PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> PREFIX prod: <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/> SELECT DISTINCT ?agent WHERE { ?agent ns1:areaOfExpertise prod:prod-cat-Transistor . }

question: Who is our Sensor expert?
query: PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT DISTINCT ?expert WHERE { ?expert ns1:areaOfExpertise <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/prod-cat-Sensor> }

question: Who is the manager of the Data Services department?
query: PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT DISTINCT ?name WHERE { <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/empl-Elena.Herzog%40company.org> rdfs:label ?name .}

question: Which department is responsible for the Sensor Switch M558-2275045?
query: PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?deptLabel WHERE { ?dept ns1:responsibleFor <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/hw-M558-2275045> . ?dept rdfs:label ?deptLabel }

question: How many Sensor Switches do we offer?
query: PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?x) AS ?count) WHERE { ?x ns1:hasCategory <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/prod-cat-Sensor> }

question: What is the name of the Network expert from the Marketing Department?
query: PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT DISTINCT ?name WHERE { ?employee ns1:areaOfExpertise <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/prod-cat-Network> ; ns1:memberOf <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/dept-85880> ; rdfs:label ?name }

question: Which departments have Transducer Experts?
query: PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT DISTINCT ?dept WHERE { ?empl ns1:areaOfExpertise <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/prod-cat-Transducer> . ?empl ns1:memberOf ?dept . ?dept a ns1:Department . }

question: Which supplier are available to deliver Compensators?
query: PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> ASK WHERE { ?compensator ns1:hasCategory <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/prod-cat-Compensator> . ?compensator ns1:hasSupplier ?supplier . }

question: How many suppliers do we have in France?
query: PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?supplier) AS ?count) WHERE { ?supplier a ns1:Supplier ; ns1:addressCountry 'France' }

question: Which supplier in France delivers Compensators?
query: PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT DISTINCT ?supplier ?name WHERE { ?supplier a ns1:Supplier ; ns1:country <http://dbpedia.org/resource/France> ; rdfs:label ?name . ?product ns1:hasSupplier ?supplier ; ns1:hasCategory <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/prod-cat-Compensator> . }

question: What is the cheapest Encoder we can get from a french or german supplier?
query: PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT ?priceValue WHERE { <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/price-hw-E395-9906117-EUR> ns1:amount ?priceValue }

question: Do we have suppliers in Toulouse?
query: PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> PREFIX dbpedia: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> SELECT ?supplier ?location ?city WHERE { ?supplier a ns1:Supplier ; ns1:country ?location . ?location dbpedia:capital ?city . FILTER(?location = <http://dbpedia.org/resource/France>) }

question: Which suppliers do we have in Toulouse?
query: PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT DISTINCT ?supplier ?name WHERE { ?supplier a ns1:Supplier ; ns1:addressLocality 'Toulouse' ; ns1:name ?name }

question: What is the cheapest Oscillator we have?
query: PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?product ?priceAmount WHERE { ?product ns1:hasCategory <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/prod-cat-Oscillator> ; ns1:price ?price . ?price ns1:amount ?priceAmount . } ORDER BY ?priceAmount LIMIT 1

question: What is the most expensive service we offer?
query: PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> SELECT ?service ?price WHERE { ?service a ns1:Service . ?service ns1:price ?priceResource . ?priceResource ns1:amount ?price . } ORDER BY DESC(?price) LIMIT 1

question: Who is responsible for the most expensive service we offer?
query: PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT ?service ?price ?department ?productManager WHERE { ?service a ns1:Service . ?service ns1:price ?price . ?price ns1:amount ?priceAmount . ?department ns1:responsibleFor ?service . ?service ns1:hasProductManager ?productManager . } ORDER BY DESC(?priceAmount) LIMIT 1

question: What is the heaviest coil that does not exceed a base area of 15x15 milimeter?
query: PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?coil ?weight ?width ?height WHERE { ?coil ns1:hasCategory <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/prod-cat-Coil> ; ns1:weight_g ?weight ; ns1:width_mm ?width ; ns1:height_mm ?height . FILTER (?width * ?height <= 225) } ORDER BY DESC(?weight) LIMIT 1

question: What products are compatible with the U990 LCD Inductor?
query: PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT DISTINCT ?compatibleProduct WHERE { <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/hw-U990-5234138> ns1:compatibleProduct ?compatibleProduct . }

question: What products can I get from US suppliers that are compatible with the U990 LCD Inductor?
query: PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT DISTINCT ?product ?supplier ?country WHERE { ?supplier ns1:country ?country . ?country = <http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States> . ?product ns1:hasSupplier ?supplier . ?product ns1:compatibleProduct <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/hw-U990-5234138> . }

question: What is the pontiometer with the smallest volume?
Which coil has the highest density?
query: PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> SELECT ?coil ?density WHERE { ?coil a ns1:Hardware ; ns1:hasCategory <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/prod-cat-Coil> ; ns1:weight_g ?weight ; ns1:height_mm ?height ; ns1:width_mm ?width ; ns1:depth_mm ?depth . BIND (?weight / (?height * ?width * ?depth / 1000 / 1000 / 1000) AS ?density) } ORDER BY DESC(?density) LIMIT 1

question: In which cities are our US suppliers for LCDs?
query: PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> PREFIX ns2: <http://www.w3.org/2003/01/geo/wgs84_pos#> SELECT DISTINCT ?supplier ?city WHERE { ?supplier a ns1:Supplier ; ns1:addressCountry 'United States' ; ns1:addressCountryCode 'US' ; ns1:addressLocality ?city . ?product ns1:hasSupplier ?supplier ; ns1:hasCategory <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/prod-cat-LCD> . }

question: Give me a phone directory of everyone on staff who does not manage anyone, I need name, email, and phone, sorted by name?
query: PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> SELECT DISTINCT ?name ?email ?phone WHERE { ?employee a ns1:Employee . OPTIONAL { ?employee foaf:name ?name . } ?employee ns1:email ?email . ?employee ns1:phone ?phone . FILTER NOT EXISTS { ?manager ns1:hasDirectReport ?employee . } } ORDER BY ?name

question: Do we have any service that does apply to a BOM where parts are sourced from Russia?
query: PREFIX ns2: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT DISTINCT ?supplier ?country WHERE { ?supplier ns2:country ?country }

question: What suppliers - I need name, country and price - deliver the 6th to 10th most expensive hardware items.
query: PREFIX prod: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT ?hardwareName ?priceAmount ?supplierName ?country WHERE { ?hardware a prod:Hardware . ?hardware prod:name ?hardwareName . ?hardware prod:price ?price . ?price prod:amount ?priceAmount . ?hardware prod:hasSupplier ?supplier . ?supplier prod:country ?country . ?supplier prod:name ?supplierName . } ORDER BY DESC(?priceAmount) LIMIT 10 OFFSET 5

question: Which department have more than 5 employees? I need their names and the number of employees.
query: PREFIX : <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT ?department ?departmentName (COUNT(?employee) AS ?employeeCount) WHERE { ?employee a :Employee . ?employee :memberOf ?department . ?department :name ?departmentName . } GROUP BY ?department ?departmentName HAVING (COUNT(?employee) > 5)

question: Per product category, what's our lightest and heaviest hardware item?
query: PREFIX prod: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT ?category (MIN(?weight) AS ?minWeight) (MAX(?weight) AS ?maxWeight) WHERE { ?product a prod:Hardware ; prod:hasCategory ?category ; prod:weight_g ?weight . } GROUP BY ?category

question: For each supplier, what's the average price (in EUR) of what they sell, round reasonably?
query: PREFIX prod: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT ?supplier (AVG(?priceAmount) AS ?averagePrice) WHERE { ?product prod:hasSupplier ?supplier . ?product prod:price ?price . ?price prod:amount ?priceAmount . ?price prod:currency 'EUR' . } GROUP BY ?supplier

question: Are there departments with no manager assigned?
query: PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?d WHERE { ?d a <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/Department> . FILTER NOT EXISTS { ?p <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/responsibleFor> ?d . ?p <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/hasProductManager> ?m } }

question: I need to update my supplier rolodex, give me every supplier's name and all address details.
query: PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT DISTINCT ?name ?addressCountry ?addressLocality ?addressText ?addressCountryCode WHERE { ?supplier a <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/Supplier> . ?supplier <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/name> ?name . OPTIONAL { ?supplier <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/addressCountry> ?addressCountry . } OPTIONAL { ?supplier <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/addressLocality> ?addressLocality . } OPTIONAL { ?supplier <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/addressText> ?addressText . } OPTIONAL { ?supplier <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/addressCountryCode> ?addressCountryCode . } }

question: For every product, list what other products it is compatible with and the price differences between both.
query: PREFIX prod: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT DISTINCT ?product WHERE { ?product a prod:Product . }

question: Which area of expertise is most relevant among our products, what are the top three skills?
query: PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT DISTINCT ?areaOfExpertise WHERE { ?agent rdf:type <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/Agent> . ?agent <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/areaOfExpertise> ?areaOfExpertise . }

question: For each Bill of Material, how many parts does it contain and what is the total material quantity — show me only those BOMs exceeding 600 total items and order them descending.
query: PREFIX prod: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT ?bom (COUNT(?part) AS ?numParts) (SUM(?quantity) AS ?totalQuantity) WHERE { ?bom a prod:BillOfMaterial . ?bom prod:hasBomPart ?bomPart . ?bomPart prod:hasPart ?part . ?bomPart prod:quantity ?quantity . } GROUP BY ?bom HAVING (SUM(?quantity) > 600) ORDER BY DESC(?totalQuantity)

question: I want to update my contact list, for each Employee give me name, email, phone number and the department they belong to as well as their direct report.
query: PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX prod: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT DISTINCT ?name ?email ?phone ?department ?directReport WHERE { ?employee a prod:Employee . ?employee prod:name ?name . ?employee prod:email ?email . ?employee prod:phone ?phone . ?employee prod:memberOf ?dept . ?dept a prod:Department . ?dept prod:name ?department . ?employee prod:hasManager ?manager . ?manager a prod:Manager . ?manager prod:name ?directReport . }

question: Which hardware items are wider than they are tall, and have a depth under 50 mm? List their dimensions.
query: PREFIX prod-vocab: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT DISTINCT ?item ?width ?height ?depth WHERE { ?item a prod-vocab:Hardware ; prod-vocab:width_mm ?width ; prod-vocab:height_mm ?height ; prod-vocab:depth_mm ?depth . FILTER (?width > ?height && ?depth < 50) }

question: Which hardware items - list id and name - have no active product manager?
query: PREFIX prod: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT ?id ?name WHERE { ?product a prod:Hardware ; prod:productId ?id ; prod:productName ?name . ?product prod:hasProductManager ?employee . FILTER NOT EXISTS { ?employee a prod:Employee . } }

question: For each manager, what percentage of their entire team work in the same department as the manager?
query: PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?manager (COUNT(DISTINCT ?directReportSameDepartment) AS ?countSameDepartment) (COUNT(DISTINCT ?directReport) AS ?totalDirectReports) WHERE { ?manager a <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/Manager> . ?manager <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/hasDirectReport> ?directReport . OPTIONAL { ?directReport <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/memberOf> ?department . ?manager <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/memberOf> ?department . BIND(?directReport AS ?directReportSameDepartment) } } GROUP BY ?manager

question: Which Bill-of-Material has the highest average unit cost of its hardware parts, and what is that average?
query: PREFIX prod: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT ?bom (AVG(?priceAmount) AS ?avgPrice) WHERE { ?bom a prod:BillOfMaterial . ?bom prod:hasBomPart ?bomPart . ?bomPart prod:hasPart ?product . ?product a prod:Hardware . ?product prod:price ?price . ?price prod:amount ?priceAmount } GROUP BY ?bom ORDER BY DESC(?avgPrice) LIMIT 1

question: Show me any cycles of product compatibility — i.e. product A says it's compatible with B, and B says it's compatible with A (mutual pairs).
query: PREFIX prod-vocab: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT DISTINCT ?productA ?productB WHERE { ?productA prod-vocab:compatibleProduct ?productB . ?productB prod-vocab:compatibleProduct ?productA . }

question: Which hardware items have dimensions in the top 10 % of all widths, and what are their IDs, names and widths?
query: PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> SELECT ?item ?name ?width WHERE { ?item a ns1:Hardware ; ns1:width_mm ?width . ?item ns1:name ?name . FILTER(xsd:decimal(?width)) } ORDER BY DESC(?width) LIMIT 10

question: Which supplier delivers the most reliable Inductor?
query: PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?supplier ?reliabilityIndex WHERE { ?hardware a ns1:Hardware . ?hardware ns1:hasCategory <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/prod-cat-Inductor> . ?hardware ns1:reliabilityIndex ?reliabilityIndex . ?hardware ns1:hasSupplier ?supplier . } ORDER BY DESC(?reliabilityIndex) LIMIT 1

question: What are the top 5 suppliers with best average reliability over their products.
query: PREFIX prod: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT ?supplier (AVG(?reliabilityIndex) AS ?avgReliability) WHERE { ?product prod:hasSupplier ?supplier . ?product prod:reliabilityIndex ?reliabilityIndex . } GROUP BY ?supplier ORDER BY DESC(?avgReliability) LIMIT 5

question: From which countries are the BOM parts of our SkySync MechWave delivered?
query: PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT DISTINCT ?country WHERE { <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/bom-17> ns1:hasBomPart ?bomPart . ?bomPart ns1:hasPart ?hw . ?hw ns1:hasSupplier ?suppl . ?suppl ns1:addressCountry ?country }

question: Show me all BOMs which have at least on part from a polish supplier.
query: PREFIX : <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?bom WHERE { ?bom a :BillOfMaterial . ?bom :hasBomPart ?bomPart . ?bomPart :hasPart ?product . ?product :hasSupplier ?supplier . ?supplier :country ?country . FILTER EXISTS { ?country rdfs:label ?label . FILTER(langMatches(lang(?label), 'en')) . FILTER(regex(?label, 'Poland', 'i')) } }

question: How many suppliers can deliver alternative compatible products for the K367 Strain Encoder?
query: PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> SELECT DISTINCT ?supplier WHERE { ?product ns1:compatibleProduct <http://ld.company.org/prod-instances/hw-K367-1320550> . ?product ns1:hasSupplier ?supplier .}

question: Which department is resposible for the most product and how many product are this?
query: PREFIX ns1: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?department (COUNT(?product) AS ?productCount) WHERE { ?department a ns1:Department . ?department ns1:responsibleFor ?product . } GROUP BY ?department ORDER BY DESC(?productCount) LIMIT 1
